{
  "info": {
    "name": "12 — Dashboard",
    "description": "DashboardController — GET /api/dashboard/{patientId}.\n\nThe dashboard aggregates 10+ FHIR resource types in one response. This collection creates a complete patient record (Practitioner, Patient, 3 Encounters, Vitals, Condition, Medication, ServiceRequest, Goal, CarePlan, Appointment) before testing the endpoint.\n\nLatest vitals: systolic 141 (above 140 warn threshold) → verifies that snapshot.alerts contains a warning and latestVitals.systolicBp.flagged is true.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "practitionerId",   "value": "" },
    { "key": "patientId",        "value": "" },
    { "key": "encounterId1",     "value": "" },
    { "key": "encounterId2",     "value": "" },
    { "key": "encounterId3",     "value": "" },
    { "key": "serviceRequestId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "conditionId",      "value": "" },
    { "key": "goalId",           "value": "" }
  ],
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "const token = pm.environment.get('BEARER_TOKEN');",
          "if (token) {",
          "  pm.request.headers.add({ key: 'Authorization', value: 'Bearer ' + token });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
